<span id="freeTextContainer16568052102337779953">I loved this text book mystery.<br/><br/>It was a refreshing departure from the usual build to a murder and then the investigation! Here we&apos;ve had the murder, the investigation and now we are straight in to finding the real killer.<br/><br/>A great set of village characters, wonderfully discribed locations and the usual amount of Agatha Christie twists and turns all with a good dose of humour.<br/><br/>Absolutely loved it.</span>
  <span id="freeText16568052102337779953" style="display:none">I loved this text book mystery.<br /><br />It was a refreshing departure from the usual build to a murder and then the investigation! Here we've had the murder, the investigation and now we are straight in to finding the real killer.<br /><br />A great set of village characters, wonderfully discribed locations and the usual amount of Agatha Christie twists and turns all with a good dose of humour.<br /><br />Absolutely loved it.</span>
